snippet.title: Under What? - Official Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Download for FREE: 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1114260/Under_What/
Itch: https://gartman.itch.io/underwhat

This visual novel is absolutely free (so if you think to sell it to someone, do not forget to share the earnings). It doesn’t require on-time spell casting and late game artefacts. It is recommended in a relaxed atmosphere with a cup of tea.

I would call this project an interactive comic rather than a visual novel or game. I spent much more time on development than I thought. I hope you will enjoy it!

Facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/daniilgartman/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/danygartman/

Portfolio: 
https://www.behance.net/gartman
https://dribbble.com/dangartman

Editing and translation​:

​Barbara Morrigan​​:  https://www.morriganwrites.com/


Music provided by HearWeGo (https://goo.gl/nDS3zR)
Artist: VonnBoyd
Title: Underwater
Listen on YouTube: https://youtu.be/_TcRZveNK6k
